{"tid":726295,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[哲學]宗教=科學?","createTime":"2018-07-02T09:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T03:19:19.000Z","uid":86196,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8c413bb0f00494c2c41f5d37f24b6da70b25cad7","tid":726295,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"上到大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一啲哲學堂會聽到科學係一種宗教<br />\n唔知各位巴絲點諗<br />\n我就覺得唔喺<br />\n宗教既真諦係信則有不信則無<br />\n但科學唔喺你唔信就唔存在<br />\n例如你唔會大嗌一句我唔信有重力跟住跳樓就唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但偏偏好多人喺要話科學係一種宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科學既真諦取決於觀察，假設，實驗，分析，結論<br />\n但我睇唔出有邊個step宗教喺有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知你地點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無意冒犯，總覺得哩句係啲讀唔成理科既文科仔先會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛恩斯坦好似講過類似既嘢(咩宗教無科學就xxx,科學無宗突就yyy)，但唔代表佢講既嘢就一定係啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc0382fd3e73346c2851c45ff154b93e34f6797","tid":726295,"uid":77164,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會講緊科學都係一種信仰"},{"pid":"1b02811536c88179588cff2e649dfd701251a73c","tid":726295,"uid":86196,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ddc0382fd3e73346c2851c45ff154b93e34f6797","tid":726295,"uid":77164,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會講緊科學都係一種信仰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"但唔喺你唔信就無喎，重力個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e758a05c287446fcddd465ceb57fbe057a2d60f6","tid":726295,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"